    Class Description
    CachingJobCatalog
    A JobCatalog decorator that caches all JobSpecs in memory.
    FSJobCatalog
    The job Catalog for file system to persist the job configuration information.

    ImmutableFSJobCatalog

    Simple implementation of a Gobblin job catalog that stores all JobSpecs in memory.
    JobCatalogBase
    An abstract base for JobCatalogs implementing boilerplate methods (metrics, listeners, etc.)

    A helper class to manage a list of JobCatalogListeners for a JobCatalog.

    Implements a write-through cache of a decorated JobCatalog
    MutableJobCatalogBase
    A base for MutableJobCatalogs.
    NonObservingFSJobCatalog
    The job Catalog for file system to persist the job configuration information.

    A Decorator for JobCatalog that loads JobTemplates from classpath (resources and classes).
    StaticJobCatalog
    A JobCatalog with a static collection of JobSpecs defined at construction time.
